OL,3,CGovernment drops Chagos Islands deal
OL,4,Cfollowing Trump criticism
OL,6,FThe government has shelved the
OL,7,Fcontroversial Chagos Islands deal
OL,8,Ffollowing backlash from US President
OL,9,FTrump, ITV News understands.
OL,11,FThe deal would return sovereignty of
OL,12,Fthe Chagos Islands to Mauritius and
OL,13,Fsee the UK pay to lease the island,
OL,14,Fwhich is home to the joint UK-US Diego
OL,15,FGarcia military base on the island, at
OL,16,Fthe cost of #101 million per year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
