FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775945463
OL,3,CGovernment drops Chagos Islands deal
OL,4,Cfollowing Trump criticism
OL,6,FIt follows a 2019 ruling by the
OL,7,FInternational Court of Justice (ICJ)
OL,8,Fwhich stated the UK was "under an
OL,9,Fobligation to bring to an end its
OL,10,Fadministration of the archipelago".
OL,12,FIn February, the US State Department
OL,13,Fsaid it backed the deal, only for
OL,14,FDonald Trump to accuse the UK of
OL,15,F"making a big mistake" the next day.
OL,17,FITV News understands that the UK
OL,18,Fgovernment has been forced to put the
OL,19,Fdeal on pause, as they haven't got the
OL,20,Ffull support they require from the US.
OL,26,@pD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
