OL,3,CGovernment drops Chagos Islands deal
OL,4,Cfollowing Trump criticism
OL,6,FIt will likely be causing a great deal
OL,7,Fof frustration across government as
OL,8,Fthe special relationship is already
OL,9,Funder strain following Donald Trump's
OL,10,Fcriticism of Keir Starmer for not
OL,11,Finvolving the UK in the Iran war.
OL,13,FInitially, Trump had described the
OL,14,Fdeal as "the best" call Starmer could
OL,15,Fmake. But he later described it as "a
OL,16,Fbig mistake", and has since cited
OL,17,Fnational and international security
OL,18,Fconcerns.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
