OL,3,CGovernment drops Chagos Islands deal
OL,4,Cfollowing Trump criticism
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA government spokesperson said: "Diego
OL,12,FGarcia is a key strategic military
OL,13,Fasset for both the UK and the US.
OL,14,FEnsuring its long-term operational
OL,15,Fsecurity is and will continue to be
OL,16,Four priority ` it is the entire reason
OL,17,Ffor the deal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
