PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775945463
OL,3,CGovernment drops Chagos Islands deal
OL,4,Cfollowing Trump criticism
OL,6,F"We continue to believe the agreement
OL,7,Fis the best way to protect the long-
OL,8,Fterm future of the base, but we have
OL,9,Falways said we would only proceed with
OL,10,Fthe deal if it has US support.
OL,12,F"We are continuing to engage with the
OL,13,FUS and Mauritius."
OL,15,FThe Conservative Party has hailed the
OL,16,Fdecision as their own victory, with
OL,17,Fparty leader Kemi Badenoch saying they
OL,18,F"led the fight against it from day
OL,19,Fone", and the deal belongs in "the ash
OL,20,Fheap of victory".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
