OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1775945463
OL,3,CGovernment drops Chagos Islands deal
OL,4,Cfollowing Trump criticism
OL,6,FWriting on social media, Badenoch
OL,7,Fsaid: "That it took so long is another
OL,8,Fdamning indictment of a prime
OL,9,Fminister, who fought to hand over
OL,10,FBritish sovereign territory and pay
OL,11,F#35 billion to use a crucial military
OL,12,Fbase which was already ours".
OL,14,FIt was the Conservative government
OL,15,Funder Rishi Sunak that began the
OL,16,Fnegotiations to return the Islands.
OL,17,FStarmer's Labour government finalised
OL,18,Fthe deal in May 2025. and Starmer's
OL,19,FLabour government finalised the deal,
OL,20,Fannouncing it in May 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
